          "reviewBody": "Don't go for this school! I got my child's admission here. They took a bulk of fees in advance! Due to covid and Lockdown, Schools got closed and my child couldn't attend a single day neither physically, nor online. Then we moved out of the city. But they didn't refund a single penny. Didn't even let us communicate to Principal. Just vandalising hard-earned money of parents. Such an unprofessional behaviour!!",
          "publisher": {
