          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Am a very happy parent.\n\nSaw my son evolve positively after he joined MMI Gurgaon and he looked forward to going there every morning.\n\nThe attention and care right from the guards, didi’s, reception staff, teachers and principal is very genuine.\n\nLooking at my son’s development and the culture in MMI, I decided to put my daughter also here and honestly, the above mentioned facts still hold true. My daughter is super happy and like my son, always looks forward to going to school in the morning. Good thing is that so many teachers and staff are still there and this speaks well of the school.\n\nAm glad both my kids have had a base here.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
